OL,3,CPolice uncover gun as part of murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation into death of Rikki Berry
OL,6,FPolice have uncovered a gun and
OL,7,Fammunition as part of a murder
OL,8,Finvestigation into the shooting of a
OL,9,Fdad.
OL,11,FRikki Berry, known locally as 'Nuggy',
OL,12,Fwas shot in his front garden on
OL,13,FQuarryside Drive in Kirkby,
OL,14,FMerseyside, just after 6.30pm on
OL,15,FWednesday 17 July.
OL,17,FOfficers attended the scene and he was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital by paramedics where
OL,19,Fhe died a short time later.
