OL,3,CPolice uncover gun as part of murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation into death of Rikki Berry
OL,6,FMerseyside Police cordoned off
OL,7,Fwasteland close to Domingo Drive on
OL,8,FThursday 18 July, a mile away from the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FOfficers found a revolver and
OL,12,Fammunition which have been
OL,13,Fforensically recovered, however, it is
OL,14,Fcurrently unclear whether it is the
OL,15,Fgun used to kill Mr Berry.
OL,17,FPolice said a 20-year-old man from
OL,18,FKirkby officers who had been arrested
OL,19,Fon suspicion of murder has since been
OL,20,Fbailed.
