OL,3,CPolice uncover gun as part of murder
OL,4,Cinvestigation into death of Rikki Berry
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector (DCI) Phil
OL,7,FAtkinson from our Firearms
OL,8,FInvestigation Team (FIT): "As with all
OL,9,Fsuch recoveries, forensic work will
OL,10,Fnow take place to establish if this
OL,11,Fweapon has been used in any firearms
OL,12,Fincidents, either in Merseyside or
OL,13,Ffurther afield.
OL,15,F"We cannot confirm at this stage if
OL,16,Fthe weapon has any connection to the
OL,17,Fmurder of Rikki Berry but the relevant
OL,18,Fenquiries will be made.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
