OL,6,F"To remove any viable firearm from
OL,7,Fcirculation is of course good news for
OL,8,Four communities, and we will continue
OL,9,Fto respond to all information which
OL,10,Fcomes our way in relation to the
OL,11,Fpossession, use and storage of
OL,12,Fweapons."
OL,14,FDCI Atkinson continued: "Key to this
OL,15,Fis information from those communities
OL,16,Fwho can be seriously affected by
OL,17,Fviolent crime where they are.
